resources.string: Media content will start playing soon

Start with a warmup. A sample warmup might be 
 - 5 minutes on a bike 
 - 5 side shuffles each way 
 - 3 push-ups, holding the bottom for 3 seconds 
 - 3 spidermans each side 
 - 20 band pull-aparts or facepulls 
 - 3x3-5 long jump, box jump, or medicine ball or wall ball throws 
 
 Once you're warmed up, fling content from the Home Gym TV app on your phone
